OL,3,CNo evidence of police collusion in
OL,4,C1978 La Mon bombing, says ombudsman
OL,6,FThere was no evidence of police
OL,7,Fcollusion in the investigation into
OL,8,Fthe 1978 La Mon House Hotel bombing,
OL,9,Fthe Police Ombudsman has said.
OL,11,FTwelve people were killed and scores
OL,12,Finjured in the atrocity when the
OL,13,FProvisional IRA exploded a bomb at the
OL,14,Fhotel on the outskirts of Belfast in
OL,15,F1978.
