OL,3,CNo evidence of police collusion in
OL,4,C1978 La Mon bombing, says ombudsman
OL,6,FHe said: "The substantial police
OL,7,Finvestigation files, associated
OL,8,Fdocumentation and intelligence records
OL,9,Freviewed by this office, together with
OL,10,Fexplanatory accounts from a number of
OL,11,Fformer police officers and other
OL,12,Finquiries, lead me to conclude that
OL,13,Fthere was earnest endeavour by the RUC
OL,14,Fto bring those responsible for the
OL,15,Fbombing of La Mon House to justice.
