OL,3,CNo evidence of police collusion in
OL,4,C1978 La Mon bombing, says ombudsman
OL,6,F"However, maintenance of the
OL,7,Finvestigation did not have the same
OL,8,Frigour and this manifested in the loss
OL,9,Fof investigative material and the
OL,10,Ffailure to interview the person
OL,11,Farrested in 1991 in relation to the
OL,12,Fbombing.
OL,14,F"I am of the view, based on all
OL,15,Favailable evidence and information,
OL,16,Fthat collusive behaviours were not a
OL,17,Ffeature of this RUC investigation.
