OL,3,CNo evidence of police collusion in
OL,4,C1978 La Mon bombing, says ombudsman
OL,6,FOne of the men was convicted of 12
OL,7,Fcounts of manslaughter in 1981, while
OL,8,Fthe other was acquitted during his
OL,9,Ftrial in 1980 after he alleged he had
OL,10,Fbeen assaulted by police while in
OL,11,Fcustody.
OL,13,FAt the 1980 trial, the judge said he
OL,14,Fcould not be satisfied beyond
OL,15,Freasonable doubt that the man's
OL,16,Fstatements had not been "adduced by
OL,17,Ftorture or inhuman or degrading
OL,18,Ftreatment" and the statements were
OL,19,Fexcluded.
