OL,6,FThe case was dismissed in the absence
OL,7,Fof other evidence.
OL,9,FMr Holmes said the judge's comments
OL,10,Fand trial outcome pointed to "a
OL,11,Fviolation of the rule of law by the
OL,12,Fpolice officers involved".
OL,14,FHe also said a loss of records and
OL,15,Fexhibits from the original
OL,16,Finvestigation was "frustrating" and
OL,17,Faffected investigators ability to
OL,18,Fproperly assess the RUC's response.
