OL,4,C1978 La Mon bombing, says ombudsman
OL,6,FMr Holmes said: "My ability to provide
OL,7,Fa definitive view on the effectiveness
OL,8,Fof the RUC investigation, including
OL,9,Fwhether all appropriate lines of
OL,10,Finquiry were pursued, has been
OL,11,Fhindered by the unavailability of
OL,12,Fcertain documentation generated by the
OL,13,Finvestigation.
OL,15,F"It has not been possible to establish
OL,16,Fthe circumstances in which these
OL,17,Frecords were lost. However, this is a
OL,18,Frecurring, systemic issue in legacy
OL,19,Fcases and is not unique to this
OL,20,Finvestigation."
