OL,3,CNo evidence of police collusion in
OL,4,C1978 La Mon bombing, says ombudsman
OL,6,F"More than 100 detectives were
OL,7,Finvolved in the murder investigation
OL,8,Fand almost 400 statements were
OL,9,Frecorded. Scenes were identified and
OL,10,Fexhibits seized, and forensic
OL,11,Fexaminations took place.
OL,13,F"In the context of the significant
OL,14,Fpressures and challenges faced by the
OL,15,FRUC at that time, I am of the view
OL,16,Fthat the investigation was well
OL,17,Fresourced and received direction from
OL,18,Fthe highest levels of the RUC."
