OL,4,C1978 La Mon bombing, says ombudsman
OL,6,FThe PSNI said in a statement it is
OL,7,Faware of the "hurt and anger" of the
OL,8,Ffamilies affected by the La Mon
OL,9,Fatrocity.
OL,11,FAssistant Chief Constable Ryan
OL,12,FHenderson, of the Justice branch, said
OL,13,Fthe organisation's thoughts are with
OL,14,Fthe families and friends of those
OL,15,Fkilled and injured in the "cowardly
OL,16,Fattack on innocent people socialising
OL,17,Fon a night out".
