OL,3,CNo evidence of police collusion in
OL,4,C1978 La Mon bombing, says ombudsman
OL,6,F"We are very aware of the hurt and
OL,7,Fanger still being felt by the families
OL,8,Fof all those who were affected by this
OL,9,Findiscriminate bomb attack and we
OL,10,Fextend our sincere sympathies to all
OL,11,Fthose families," he said.
OL,13,F"We acknowledge the historic issues
OL,14,Fidentified in the report concerning
OL,15,Frecords management in this
OL,16,Finvestigation, however, this was at a
OL,17,Ftime that predated the introduction of
OL,18,Fthe computerised Home Office Large
OL,19,FMajor Enquiry System (Holmes).
