OL,3,CNo evidence of police collusion in
OL,4,C1978 La Mon bombing, says ombudsman
OL,6,F"While the Police Ombudsman's report
OL,7,Fhas identified some investigative
OL,8,Ffailings, it also highlights that the
OL,9,Finvestigation was well-resourced,
OL,10,Fcomprehensive and effective.
OL,12,F"The report has found that police held
OL,13,Fno intelligence prior to the attack
OL,14,Fthat could have prevented it and also
OL,15,Ffound that there was no evidence that
OL,16,Fany persons were protected from
OL,17,Fprosecution.
