OL,3,CNo evidence of police collusion in
OL,4,C1978 La Mon bombing, says ombudsman
OL,6,F"I would also like to reflect on the
OL,7,Fcourage, compassion and
OL,8,Fprofessionalism and of the police
OL,9,Fofficers who responded to the scene of
OL,10,Fthe bombing.
OL,12,F"The difficult and challenging
OL,13,Fcircumstances they faced when dealing
OL,14,Fwith the victims and survivors
OL,15,Frepresented the highest of standards
OL,16,Fand I welcome the fact that the Police
OL,17,FOmbudsman has highlighted this in the
OL,18,Freport."
